{"tid":421424,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲加力壓費Sir創紀錄","createTime":"2017-10-02T08:41:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-02T08:53:02.000Z","uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ee882245ba71325bfd27770172c2e04ada6e8765","tid":421424,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T08:41:53.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴今仗16分鐘由蒙利爾打開缺口，至下半場11分鐘由伊禾比再入1球奠定勝局，最後順利以2：0勝出全取3分。連同今次擊敗白禮頓，雲格已經在英超擊敗過45支不同球隊，超越前曼聯傳奇主帥費格遜44隊的紀錄。而雲格執教英超後首個「受害者」為布力般流浪，時間已經要追溯至1996年10月。<br />\n<br />\n45 - Arsene Wenger has now beaten 45 different opponents in the @premierleague, more than any other manager (Alex Ferguson, 44). Stalwart. <a href=\"http://pic.twitter.com/Jx4KakgPCn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.twitter.com%2FJx4KakgPCn&d=5%2FnICMbkZLsf25Oos8gElJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=00cb1096\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">pic.twitter.com/Jx4KakgPCn</a><br />\n&mdash; OptaJoe (@OptaJoe) October 1, 2017<br />\n雲格過去領阿仙奴贏過包括聯賽冠軍在內等不同錦標，不過近年球隊表現停滯不前，去季更有大量球迷呼籲這名法國老帥下台，不過他最終仍獲會方信任續約2年。<br />\n<br />\n雲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30be17d4b38bdf25b7d6e5f62b25d49ef981356b","tid":421424,"uid":993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T08:50:39.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"cb78188eb765d193ffcbe79bed7d929ba4853f35","tid":421424,"uid":136430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T08:53:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n永續雲加"}]}